TY  - JOUR
TI  - A Test for Misspecification in the Censored Normal Model
AU  - Nelson, Forrest D.
AB  - [Estimates of parameters in Tobit and other models for limited, truncated and censored dependent variables are not robust against misspecification. A test of the standard assumptions against a general misspecified alternative in the univariate censored normal model is derived and extended to the Tobit regression case. Computational ease and freedom from specification of a specific alternative hypothesis are primary attractions of the test.]
